DAT
id=qid::label=str::text=lstr::
26197::$$$message_0225_0000_0000$$$::I should ask about those clothes she's wearing.::
26198::$$$message_0225_0001_0000$$$::"So, Saber, I want to ask you something."[lr]::
26199::$$$message_0225_0001_0001$$$::"Yes, what is it?"[lr]::
26200::$$$message_0225_0001_0002$$$::"Where did you get those clothes? You look completely different than yesterday, so you kinda caught me off guard."[lr]::
26201::$$$message_0225_0001_0003$$$::Actually, I'm still bewildered.::
26202::$$$message_0225_0002_0000$$$::"Rin provided them for me. She thought it would be best that I avoid attracting attention, as I am unable to return to spirit form."[lr]::
26203::$$$message_0225_0002_0001$$$::"I see. I had no idea."::
26204::$$$message_0225_0003_0000$$$::"What about them?"[lr]::
26205::$$$message_0225_0003_0001$$$::"Uh, nothing... Don't worry about it." [lr]::
26206::$$$message_0225_0003_0002$$$::I want to tell her they look good on her, but I manage to stop myself.[lr]::
26207::$$$message_0225_0003_0003$$$::If I said something like that, I'd probably go beet red.::
26208::$$$message_0225_0004_0000$$$::"Shirou?"[lr]::
26209::$$$message_0225_0004_0001$$$::"Uh...I...well, yeah...you know...um...yesterday's armor![lr]::
26210::$$$message_0225_0004_0002$$$::Yeah...! I was just wondering what happened to your armor!"::
26211::$$$message_0225_0005_0000$$$::"There is no need to worry about that. There are no rules for wearing armor, so I have it off while I am wearing these clothes.[lr]::
26212::$$$message_0225_0005_0001$$$::That armor is created from my magical energy. I can call for it as needed."::
26213::$$$message_0225_0006_0000$$$::[font italic=true]...[font italic=false][lr]::
26214::$$$message_0225_0006_0001$$$::I can only respond with amazement.[lr]::
26215::$$$message_0225_0006_0002$$$::...Anyway, there's no doubt she'd draw a lot of attention going around in that armor.[lr]::
26216::$$$message_0225_0006_0003$$$::But with Saber wearing something like that, I can probably make up some story to the neighbors that she's a distant relative of my old man or something.[lr]::
26217::$$$message_0225_0006_0004$$$::...Well actually, I have to do that anyway.::ëK